{"tid":818453,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求解]房ROUTER WIFI 成日斷線","createTime":"2018-09-14T06:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T10:59:31.000Z","uid":69010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"89a14314523bc1db449e5f8b9eb121f238df3c65","tid":818453,"uid":69010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T06:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/14/141956_57c3eae8259bf9f5f78a41f2874fb26c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F14%2F141956_57c3eae8259bf9f5f78a41f2874fb26c.jpg&h=4b6a3319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連住LAN線既電腦有600MB左右既, <br />\n<br />\n但手機連WIFI只有3MB左右,<br />\n<br />\n用LAN線連完全冇問題，廳既WIFI亦好穩定，但房既WIFI 就成日斷線<br />\n<br />\n試過將2部ROUTER掉轉,但情況一樣,所有野都冇變<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已試過:<br />\n改無線模式,頻道,限制IP最多去到192.168.1.5,<br />\n運作模式(無線路由器模式,AP MODE),更新ROUTER<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到底係咩原因,令到房既WIFI成日斷線?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔想成日都要出廳打機.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185e45f18cdf1876c139f32166378d6de1bee61c","tid":818453,"uid":55369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T07:14:31.000Z","msg":"拉條線入房？"},{"pid":"89d0c9d2b146f05fca9a4dda3cf5bc18ce91da4c","tid":818453,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T07:56:03.000Z","msg":"ap mode有問題，如果拉唔到線入房，不如用mesh router，收得好過ap"},{"pid":"5e237731f7299761d2c20a168998c2a93b6d383c","tid":818453,"uid":69010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"185e45f18cdf1876c139f32166378d6de1bee61c","tid":818453,"uid":55369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T07:14:31.000Z","msg":"拉條線入房？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:12:38.000Z","msg":"係 拉左線入房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"